:26.000Z","msg":"83<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6968ad5cee934bda84e03a37d21981affb3d4fd8","tid":1831772,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"男姓女乳症<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b74337c26340365273adff1942ebee87b8b52e","tid":1831772,"uid":49336,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgmSMhE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgmSMhE.gif&h=63c1caee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n<br />\n「你癡左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n<br />\n成個小醜咁係到穀佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"757f23a32e43a79365ed0a55146f92166005cb80","tid":1831772,"uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"723861164e0391387ff3e9e038e6d1360b805073","tid":1831772,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:11:19.000Z","msg":"墮lin"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"八廿幾係人都墮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee856d9a036b0cd128e426aa849ec3cc3958eeaf","tid":1831772,"uid":70878,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:13:36.000Z","msg":"鍾南山後，活死人墓，神鵰俠侶，絕跡江湖。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif